h4. Context

After the User clicks on the Apple Pay button, initiate Payment processing and enable biometric authorization. 

h4. Scope

Users are able to see the “ Pay with touchID/ FaceID” button on the payment sheet

h4. Tasks

# On the successful display of Payment sheet, capture ApplePayValidateMerchantEvent successfully
# Create an opaque Apple Pay session
# Complete Apple merchant validation- This is the validation done by Apple to confirm XXXX is a valid merchant. 

!image-20220804-054702.png|width=1334,height=247!

h4. Out of scope:

# ApplePayValidate Merchant event is not received
# Any other errors due to failure in apple merchant validation
